<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 14:06:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>这些以色列儿童在哈马斯袭击中幸存下来。他们努力再次成为孩子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-israeli-children-survived-the-hamas-attack-they-struggle-to-be-kids-again/0000018c-105f-dd2e-a5ae-d35fb8880000</link><description>“几个小时内我们就长大了好几年”：10 月 7 日事件中五名勇敢的年轻幸存者现在分散在以色列各地，讲述了在这场令人震惊的大屠杀中幸存下来的孩子们的故事</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 13:36:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-israeli-children-survived-the-hamas-attack-they-struggle-to-be-kids-again/0000018c-105f-dd2e-a5ae-d35fb8880000</guid></item><item><title>压力之下：以色列必须就加沙战争做出三项重大决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/under-pressure-three-fateful-decisions-israel-must-make-about-the-war-in-gaza/0000018c-1593-d19a-a3cf-7d9366eb0000</link><description>以色列在下一阶段针对加沙哈马斯的战争中面临着三大难题，其中对于内塔尼亚胡政府来说，也许没有什么比人道主义援助问题更关键和更具爆炸性了。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 13:32:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/under-pressure-three-fateful-decisions-israel-must-make-about-the-war-in-gaza/0000018c-1593-d19a-a3cf-7d9366eb0000</guid></item><item><title>所有人的目光都集中在加沙，西岸巴勒斯坦人面临着前所未有的暴力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-11-28/ty-article-podcast/with-all-eyes-on-gaza-west-bank-palestinians-are-facing-unprecedented-violence/0000018c-11e4-dd2e-a5ae-d3ef0ac20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 13:18:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-11-28/ty-article-podcast/with-all-eyes-on-gaza-west-bank-palestinians-are-facing-unprecedented-violence/0000018c-11e4-dd2e-a5ae-d3ef0ac20000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯裔以色列男子因 2021 年企图私刑处决犹太出租车司机而被判处 17 年徒刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-man-sentenced-to-17-years-for-attempted-lynching-of-jewish-cab-driver-in-2021/0000018c-15a9-dd2e-a5ae-d7ebb87f0000</link><description>23 岁的库赛·阿巴斯 (Qusai Abbas) 被一致判定在 2021 年 5 月以色列种族间骚乱期间与其他七名骚乱者企图谋杀莫尔·贾纳什维利 (Mor Janashvili)。法官称，一群暴徒试图处决贾纳什维利，只是因为他是犹太人</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 13:03:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-man-sentenced-to-17-years-for-attempted-lynching-of-jewish-cab-driver-in-2021/0000018c-15a9-dd2e-a5ae-d7ebb87f0000</guid></item><item><title>指控以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝是煽动性且危险的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/charging-israel-with-genocide-in-gaza-is-inflammatory-and-dangerous/0000018c-103d-d679-abdc-963d1ecb0000</link><description>历史学家必须以事实为指导，而不是政治议程。但当《纽约时报》的奥马尔·巴托夫指责以色列“濒临”种族灭绝和种族清洗时，他的论点是基于断言，而不是证据</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 12:05:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/charging-israel-with-genocide-in-gaza-is-inflammatory-and-dangerous/0000018c-103d-d679-abdc-963d1ecb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子因在孩子面前谋杀妻子而被判处终身监禁和六年监禁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sentenced-to-life-plus-six-years-in-prison-for-murder-of-wife-in-front-of-children/0000018c-1579-dd03-a7ff-bf79aa920000</link><description>阿米尔·拉兹是一名警察，他用绳子绑住了这对夫妇的四个孩子，阻止女儿呼救，然后刺伤戴安娜并开枪射杀了她。除了谋杀之外，他还被判殴打未成年人罪名成立，法院命令他向孩子们赔偿 285,000 谢克尔</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 12:02:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sentenced-to-life-plus-six-years-in-prison-for-murder-of-wife-in-front-of-children/0000018c-1579-dd03-a7ff-bf79aa920000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡适合在这场战争中领导以色列吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/is-netanyahu-fit-to-lead-this-war/0000018c-1584-dd2e-a5ae-d7cfbd220000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡不明白，除非以色列为“后天”制定计划，否则我们可能不得不在疯狂的战略赌博和在国际压力下投降之间做出选择</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 11:41:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/is-netanyahu-fit-to-lead-this-war/0000018c-1584-dd2e-a5ae-d7cfbd220000</guid></item><item><title>几名以色列阿拉伯妇女被列入最新的囚犯名单，以换取哈马斯的释放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/50-women-palestinian-prisoners-added-to-list-of-candidates-for-release-in-exchange-deal/0000018c-1532-dd03-a7ff-bf3a72ae0000</link><description>最新名单上的被拘留者中有 46 人在 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击后被捕。不同寻常的是，名单上的大约 20 名女性是来自该国阿拉伯社区的以色列公民，其中一些人被判犯有谋杀未遂罪</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 10:47:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/50-women-palestinian-prisoners-added-to-list-of-candidates-for-release-in-exchange-deal/0000018c-1532-dd03-a7ff-bf3a72ae0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔总理拒绝批评与哈马斯的关系，称此举是为了稳定该地区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/qatari-pm-rejects-criticism-over-relationship-with-hamas-says-its-to-stabilize-the-region/0000018c-1500-dd03-a7ff-bf3888480000</link><description>穆罕默德·阿勒萨尼在接受德国一家报纸采访时表示，他的国家“认同巴勒斯坦人民，而不是政党”。他补充说，正是多哈与哈马斯的联系促成了人质获释协议，并因长达数天的停火而“拯救了生命”</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 10:07:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/qatari-pm-rejects-criticism-over-relationship-with-hamas-says-its-to-stabilize-the-region/0000018c-1500-dd03-a7ff-bf3888480000</guid></item><item><title>在对以色列立场的压力下，拜登政府强调加沙援助努力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/biden-administration-highlights-humanitarian-aid-efforts-in-gaza-during-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-153d-d19a-a3cf-7dbd432d0000</link><description>由于白宫因支持以色列的军事目标而面临强烈批评，它现在将重点放在向加沙提供必要援助的努力上。一位官员表示，拜登、布林肯、沙利文和其他人“每天晚上都与以色列同行通电话，以解决这些问题”</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 10:01:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/biden-administration-highlights-humanitarian-aid-efforts-in-gaza-during-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-153d-d19a-a3cf-7dbd432d0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙正在发生的灾难：当人道主义援助成为你的最后一餐时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gazas-unfolding-disaster-when-humanitarian-aid-is-your-last-meal/0000018c-10c7-dd2e-a5ae-d3cf31b00000</link><description>孤儿在街上成倍增加，爆炸幸存者受到创伤，一旦停战结束，每个人都知道死亡随时可能再次从天而降。许多人没有药物，也几乎没有干净的水或食物</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 09:12:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gazas-unfolding-disaster-when-humanitarian-aid-is-your-last-meal/0000018c-10c7-dd2e-a5ae-d3cf31b00000</guid></item><item><title>6 名青少年因涉嫌参与 2020 年斩首法国教师事件而受审</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-28/ty-article/6-teenagers-go-on-trial-for-their-alleged-role-in-the-2020-beheading-of-a-french-teacher/0000018c-14d3-d19a-a3cf-7cd326180000</link><description>塞缪尔·帕蒂 (Samuel Paty) 是一名历史和地理教师，于 2020 年 10 月 16 日在巴黎西北部郊区的学校附近被一名变得激进的 18 岁车臣裔青少年杀害。袭击者随后被警方击毙</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 07:40:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-28/ty-article/6-teenagers-go-on-trial-for-their-alleged-role-in-the-2020-beheading-of-a-french-teacher/0000018c-14d3-d19a-a3cf-7cd326180000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正确地怀疑哈马斯将延迟释放人质归咎于“技术问题”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-rightly-doubts-hamas-when-its-blames-technical-issues-for-delays-freeing-hostages/0000018c-12b3-d65f-a7dd-f2f7f1140000</link><description>显而易见，哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔正试图采用“饥饿游戏”式的心理战：利用各种借口拆散父母子女、兄弟姐妹，只允许其中部分人返回以色列。</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 04:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-rightly-doubts-hamas-when-its-blames-technical-issues-for-delays-freeing-hostages/0000018c-12b3-d65f-a7dd-f2f7f1140000</guid></item><item><title>加沙北部以色列军队附近发生爆炸；中央情报局和摩萨德负责人讨论卡塔尔人质交易的下一阶段</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article-live/11-hostages-freed-from-gaza-israel-receives-list-of-10-more-to-be-released-on-tuesday/0000018c-1405-dd2e-a5ae-d74f01bf0000</link><description>以色列国防军：加沙北部发生爆炸，违反停火协议，士兵受轻伤 ■ 12 岁人质的姨妈被释放：他被迫观看 10 月 7 日囚禁暴行的录像 ■ 以色列和哈马斯同意延长停火协议额外开火两天换取20名人质 ■ 84岁以色列人质获释后入院治疗，生命垂危 ■ 自10月7日以来，以色列至少有1,200名平民和士兵被杀；超过 150 名人质仍被扣押在加沙 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：加沙有 14,854 人死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Nov 2023 03:50:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-28/ty-article-live/11-hostages-freed-from-gaza-israel-receives-list-of-10-more-to-be-released-on-tuesday/0000018c-1405-dd2e-a5ae-d74f01bf0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-28/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-12fe-d19a-a3cf-7aff49430000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 22:59:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-28/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018c-12fe-d19a-a3cf-7aff49430000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府对以色列首席银行家的攻击证明了其腐败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-28/ty-article-opinion/the-netanyahu-governments-attacks-on-israels-chief-banker-testify-to-its-corruption/0000018c-1295-d19a-a3cf-7a95d8b60002</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 22:43:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-28/ty-article-opinion/the-n